          <div class="text-7xl mb-6">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition">CAC Calculator</h3>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">True acquisition cost with 2026 benchmarks</p>
          <span class="text-accent font-bold text-xl group-hover:translate-x-3 transition">Calculate ‚Üí</span>
        </a>
        <a href="#email-roi-calculator" class="glass-card p-10 group hover:border-accent hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-400">
          <div class="text-7xl mb-6">üìß</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition">Email ROI</h3>
