        </a>
        <a href="#break-even-calculator" class="glass-card p-10 group hover:border-accent hover:-translate-y-3 transition-all duration-400">
          <div class="text-7xl mb-6">‚öñÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 group-hover:text-accent transition">Break-Even ROAS</h3>
