          <span class="text-accent font-bold text-xl group-hover:translate-x-3 transition">Calculate ‚Üí</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAC (Dark - Split) -->
  <section id="cac-calculator" class="section dark py-20">
    <div class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <h2 class="text-5xl font-black gradient-text">Customer Acquisition Cost (CAC)</h2>
        <p class="text-2xl text-white/90">Your real cost to win one customer ‚Äî benchmarked against 2026 SaaS leaders.</p>
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">How to Use</h3>
            <ol class="list-decimal pl-8 space-y-3 text-xl">
              <li>Enter total sales & marketing spend (monthly or quarterly)</li>
              <li>Enter new customers acquired in same period</li>
              <li>See your CAC + elite benchmark rating</li>
            </ol>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-accent mb-4">Real Impact</h3>
            <p class="text-xl">B2B SaaS client slashed CAC from $1,200 ‚Üí $380 in 6 months by optimizing Meta/Google targeting.</p>
            <p class="text-xl font-bold text-accent mt-4">Result: 3x faster scaling velocity</p>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold text-accent">Privacy: 100% client-side. Nothing saved or tracked.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
